        "content": "<p>Wasmtime traps. There is a open PR to codify this in the spec:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-io/pull/69\">https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-io/pull/69</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-io/pull/69\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/275dfba708dc6370e8fe0a5142def8b25cfa252f/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f373334346666316438363965316464653238383735663564656263323937383030373531363636366661393562353931613266353234333039396463333139662f576562417373656d626c792f776173692d696f2f70756c6c2f3639&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-io/pull/69\" title=\"poll: Require there to be at least one item. by badeend · Pull Request #69 · WebAssembly/wasi-io\">poll: Require there to be at least one item. by badeend · Pull Request #69 · WebAssembly/wasi-io</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Fixes #67</div></div></div>",
