    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"378155\">Dave Bakker (badeend)</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/219900-wasi/topic/How.20to.20handle.20poll.2Epoll.20.20empty.20poll.20list/near/435144954\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Wasmtime traps. There is a open PR to codify this in the spec:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-io/pull/69\">https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-io/pull/69</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Thanks. I will also go with trapping for now.</p>",
